# Xcode
#
# gitignore contributors: remember to update Global/Xcode.gitignore, Objective-C.gitignore & Swift.gitignore

## User settings
xcuserdata/

## Device specific data
*.ipa
*.bundle

## Build results
build/
DerivedData/

## Tests
*.xccheckout
*.xcresult

## Playgrounds
timeline.xctimeline
playground.xcworkspace

## Swift Package Manager
.build/
.swiftpm/

## Misc
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.lock

## Assets
Assets.xcassets/
